  "version": 1,
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.421292,
      "replayEndSec": 9.419365,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-01.0c27526f.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.445714,
      "textHash": "0c27526ff12f4412b218749705c5161146d0d515dcc72602e29c078ed446ba24",
      "narrationText": "Seadistame esimese saladuse env-režiimis. Väärtus jõuab konteineris keskkondmuutujana. Pane tähele tühja current lippu -- deklareerime, et see on täiesti uus saladus ilma eelneva väärtuseta.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-01-after.56a26874.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.127347,
      "afterTextHash": "56a26874404b6e0e1c908890336bfd10b17ae50ab2c2029d8d2883115c6c9159"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 9.419365,
      "replayEndSec": 16.481794,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-02.1fd5dfa1.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.87102,
      "textHash": "1fd5dfa17e2c02914cfd0a2fd00279fe6544bbec96e0bef82e8bb4b6ad250880",
      "narrationText": "Nüüd file-režiimi saladus. File-režiim ei pane väärtust kunagi konteineri keskkonda. See kirjutab selle failile asukohas slash run slash secrets, kasutades Dockeri standardsete saladuste mehhanismi. Eelista seda kõige tundliku jaoks.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-02-after.d52b49dc.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 7.157551,
      "afterTextHash": "d52b49dc1cb4a269f40ea878361b1342004b77ae7259a47bc530a4e16ccc7280"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 16.481794,
      "replayEndSec": 20.7282,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-03.508b05f0.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 7.079184,
      "textHash": "508b05f02a4900b5731f7d3cd012d50ca5b97c4ec6219548aa3f742def80e799",
      "narrationText": "Loetleme, mis meil on. Ainult nimed ja režiimid. Loend ei näita kunagi väärtusi, olenemata küsijast.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-03-after.54a069bd.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.597551,
      "afterTextHash": "54a069bd7032f0c857fac22577f4afe13843e6ebe1506fcdce8d4f46574afdc2"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 20.7282,
      "replayEndSec": 25.737687,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-04.187a57e9.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.714286,
      "textHash": "187a57e95d04b54528efb22241fc190fd1624356c9c7adae57093637e4435938",
      "narrationText": "Siin on osa, mis inimesi üllatab. Get tagastab räsi, mitte väärtuse. Puudub lipp, mis paneks selle lihtteksti tagastama. Puudub käsk, mis selle tagastaks. See on GitHub Actionsi mudel: ainult kirjutamiseks kujunduse järgi.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-04-after.b8c0a47c.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.675918,
      "afterTextHash": "b8c0a47cfc42eafe018a9f1dd00c5e9f37746a968c1618ff449465fda02b8ba3"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 25.737687,
      "replayEndSec": 32.972076,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-05.16555660.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.714286,
      "textHash": "16555660591255e12f336a3dabefe91481c507d6763ad1c873e778eb38e1a502",
      "narrationText": "Väärtus kadunud? Ära piilu. Roteeri. Rotate-secret lipp jätab eeltingimuse kontrolli vahele ja auditilogi märgib muudatuse tahtliku rotatsioonina. Kõva, tahtlik ja turvaline.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-05-after.8931d951.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.284082,
      "afterTextHash": "8931d9511f3792d425d34b96454e02fdf609fa224ad0ac6361a1d95fc093bc14"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-06",
      "markerIndex": 5,
      "replayStartSec": 32.972076,
      "replayEndSec": 39.065377,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-06.761f3b2a.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 6.687347,
      "textHash": "761f3b2a97ca724509afe5015256dde55216bd341b1f916a662e2a8f923c0958",
      "narrationText": "Nüüd lõppmäng. Teeme repositooriumist forki. Fork on vanemkujutise baidi haaval koopia.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-06-after.38d00158.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.552653,
      "afterTextHash": "38d0015858f5cfc1b00bda23960403f77a7b96d1bd011b81de7dc3151c73194e"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-07",
      "markerIndex": 6,
      "replayStartSec": 39.065377,
      "replayEndSec": 44.3362,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-07.5057d5d6.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.759184,
      "textHash": "5057d5d63f98dda9ae7596910caea7bd693e26e6217e4ae8eb275df1c368c8d4",
      "narrationText": "Kuid kui loetleme forki saladusi -- tühi. Stripe'i võtit pole, andmebaasi parooli pole, API tokenit pole. Fork ei saa sind imiteerida. Seepärast töötab klooni tootmine, rikku mitte midagi tegelikkuses.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-07-after.c1969fa6.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.04898,
      "afterTextHash": "c1969fa615a1ccb6c87056a3a6529cc47963c0b65726ec0b055c676f2e0ff695"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/intro.54a33bea.mp3",
      "textHash": "54a33bea59bbe638734f0a5b487d9c1d9e06e2119bd45951f9741761f59d84ef",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.907755,
      "narrationText": "Aeg panna päris mandaadid kohta, kuhu forgid ei pääse! Seadistame kaks saladust, tõestame, et need on ainult kirjutamiseks, siis forgime repo ja vaatame, kuidas need kaovad."
    },
    {
      "id": "env-trap",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/env-trap.cc1e8c54.mp3",
      "textHash": "cc1e8c54d62dd36ce082dbfb936bcfef062731cb43f739663869d066efcfa606",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.386122,
      "narrationText": "Enamik meeskondi paneb .env faili repositooriumisse, sest see on ilmne käik. Probleem on selles, et fork pärib kujutise baidi haaval koopia, nii et sinu liivakast käivitub tootmise Stripe'i võtmega ja hakkab päris klientide kaarte koormama."
    },
    {
      "id": "write-only",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/write-only.a3a6ca9d.mp3",
      "textHash": "a3a6ca9dcbaad88ae3251e32d0b96d5c914113f61173225ef664020e36626ce6",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.949388,
      "narrationText": "CLI järgib GitHub Actionsi mudelit: get tagastab räsi, mitte kunagi väärtust. Kui kaotad saladuse jälje, sa ei piilu, sa roteerid, ja auditilogi salvestab selle tahtliku muudatusena."
    },
    {
      "id": "fork-isolation",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/fork-isolation.8e502597.mp3",
      "textHash": "8e50259780909a7ccf5e8894e73b00ab85c6537eaf7dc1e570f8e6a83615b62e",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.826122,
      "narrationText": "Siin on vastutasu. Fork jagab vanema krüpteeritud andmeid, kuid saladuste hoidla on repo-põhine, nii et fork loetleb tühja ega saa interpoleerida ühtegi sinu tootmisvõtit."
    },
    {
      "id": "next-tutorial",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-managing-secrets/next-tutorial.2e771726.mp3",
      "textHash": "2e771726ff4cf7ea0712fddcc8a9f0e4f5f4643449636f9b3037212fa256ec90",
      "audioDurationSec": 5.485714,
      "narrationText": "Ja sellega on saladused lukus, kuhu forgid ei jõua. Kohtumiseni järgmises!"
    }
  ],
